<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> briefe und die noteln
                                                  <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan>, die ir
                                                  <add>uns</add> gesant habt, als
                                                  <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> von
                                                  <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Ker
                                                  <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und
                                                  <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> des
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dinstlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und mit
                                                  <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleizze. Und als
                                                  <add>dann</add> ewr gnad begert hat, schicken wir
                                                ew <expan>meist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Weynand<ex>e</ex>n,</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> doctor, dem wir
                                                  <add>also</add>
<expan>bevolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>obgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> sache
                                                  <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> mit
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czü
                                                  <expan>red<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und
                                                  <expan>bit<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hochw<ex>irdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleizzikl<ex>ich,</ex></expan> was er
                                                  <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> czü
                                                  <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan> mal an
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnad werb
                                                  <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz ir im des
                                                  <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und uns
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hochw<ex>irdikeit</ex></expan> in den und
                                                  <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sachen
                                                  <expan>genediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bevolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> sein
                                                  <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, als wir
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol
                                                  <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> und umb
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hochw<ex>irdikeit</ex></expan> czü
                                                  <expan>allenczeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>willikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>
<expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in
                                                  <expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan> pasche.</ab>
